               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Papers document expeditions by Louis-Armand Chapelier to Mauritius and Madagascar, and Nicolas Baudin to the West Indies, as well as expeditions to Egypt and India, and Pierre Clément de Laussat's planned expedition to Louisiana, later cancelled after France sold the territory to the United States.</p>
